<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id781882e5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s470aaa–2"><num value="470aaa–2">§ 470aaa–2.</num><heading> Public awareness and education program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall establish a program to increase public awareness about the significance of paleontological resources.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id781882e6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tVI/s6303">Pub. L. 111–11, title VI, § 6303</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1173">123 Stat. 1173</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
